data.description: Location between Cedartown and Rockmart in Sunset Valley. This beautiful home features a 1.45 acre lot with beautiful retaining wall and landscaping.  Two car garage provides entry to the finished basement along with side walk to a lovely front porch.  Enter a foyer with dining room to the left, Large family room with fireplace that has french doors to the very desireable deck.  The kitchen has  ample space for a breakfast area. The laundry area is also convenient. Three bedrooms and 2 baths are on the main level.  A finished basement has a family room with a bar a bonus room or bedroom with a bathroom.
